<HL>
   Canadian Bankruptcies Jump
</HL>
<DATE>
07/19/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A7
</SO>
<CO>
   CANDA
</CO>
<IN>
BANKRUPTCIES (BCY)
</IN>
<LP>
   OTTAWA -- Canadian bankruptcies rose to 4,109 in June, up
32.3% from 3,105 a year earlier, the Canadian Consumer and
Corporate Affairs Department said.
   Individual bankruptcies totaled 3,286 and business
bankruptcies totaled 823 in June.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   In the first half, bankruptcies rose 30.4% to 23,651 from
18,138 a year earlier.
</TEXT>
